{"word":"παραλογίζομαι","slug":"παραλογίζομαι","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>παραλογίζομαι</b></el> <el>(<a href='S:future tense'>fut.</a> <el>ίσομαι</el>) </el><p/><a href='S:Deponent Verb, i.e. a Verb of Middle or Passive form with Active sense'>Dep.</a>:<p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b>in keeping accounts, <i>to misreckon, miscalculate</i>, <b><a href='S:Demosthenes'>Dem.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>2. </b><i>to cheat out</i> of a thing, <i>to defraud of</i>, <a href='S:cum'>c.</a> dupl. <a href='S:accusative'>acc.</a>, <b><a href='S:Aristotle'>Arist.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b><i>to mislead by fallacious reasoning</i>, <b><a href='S:Aeschines'>Aeschin.</a></b>:—<a href='S:passive signification'><a href='S:Passive Voice'>Pass.</a></a> <i>to be so misled</i>, <b><a href='S:Aristotle'>Arist.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}